            <DOI name="Beh" desc="Read-only value, describing the behaviour of a domain logical node. It depends on the current operating mode of the logical node ('DomainLN.Mod'), and the current operating mode of the logical device that contains it ('LLN0.Mod'). Processing of the quality status ('q') of the received data is the prerequisite for correct interpretation of 'DomainLN.Beh'.">
